description: Tina, you every boy’s dream. Actually, I take that back, there is no satisfying you, if you were my girlfriend I really would need to keep all our machines in the bedroom. We all had an ear-to-ear grin shooting Tina Toy, one screaming orgasm on top of another, and when we were busy setting up for the next machine she would lie on the couch doing herself with a pocket rocket. You are welcome back any time Tina!
title: Tina Toy
